The paper describes an image-comparison technique using image compression for geological mapping and novelty detection. This involves computer vision and machine learning techniques, which are commonly associated with the computer science sub-categories of computer vision (cs.CV), robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and information retrieval (cs.IR). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
